INSERT INTO `products` VALUES (40, 'Midea Air Conditioning Unit', '<h2>Compact Air Conditioning Unit for Residential Use</h2><p>The Compact Air Conditioning Unit by Midea is designed to provide efficient and effective cooling for residential environments. With its sleek and compact design, this air conditioning unit seamlessly fits into any home setting while delivering powerful cooling performance. It is ideal for smaller spaces such as apartments, bedrooms, or home offices, where space is limited but cooling needs are essential.<br>Featuring advanced technology and user-friendly controls, this air conditioning unit ensures a comfortable living environment with minimal energy consumption.</p><br><h3>Key Features:</h3><ul><li><strong>Compact Design:</strong>Features a sleek and space-saving design that fits seamlessly into residential spaces without occupying excessive room.<br></li><li><strong>Efficient Cooling:</strong>Delivers powerful and consistent cooling to maintain a comfortable indoor climate in smaller areas.<br></li><li><strong>User-Friendly Controls:</strong>Equipped with intuitive controls and settings for easy operation and temperature adjustments.<br></li><li><strong>Energy Efficient:</strong>Designed to minimize energy consumption, providing cost-effective cooling solutions and reducing utility bills.<br></li><li><strong>Quiet Operation:</strong>Operates quietly to ensure a peaceful and undisturbed home environment.<br></li></ul><p>Perfect for residential use, the Compact Air Conditioning Unit by Midea offers effective cooling, energy efficiency, and ease of use, enhancing comfort in smaller living spaces with its advanced features and compact design.</p>', 600000.00, '1723004874_55cb268e64699c13125b.png', 'Manado', 10, NULL);
INSERT INTO `products` VALUES (41, 'Komatsu Bulldozer', '<h2>Durable Bulldozer for Heavy Construction Tasks</h2><p>The Durable Bulldozer by Komatsu is built to handle the toughest construction tasks with reliability and efficiency. Engineered for heavy-duty performance, this bulldozer is ideal for large-scale construction projects, including earth-moving, grading, and site preparation. Its robust construction and powerful engine ensure it can tackle the most demanding conditions and deliver consistent results.<br>Designed with advanced features and high durability, this bulldozer supports various heavy construction activities, providing strength and stability for complex tasks.</p><br><h3>Key Features:</h3><ul><li><strong>Heavy-Duty Construction:</strong>Built with robust materials and engineering to withstand the toughest construction environments and tasks.<br></li><li><strong>Powerful Engine:</strong>Equipped with a high-performance engine to deliver the necessary power and efficiency for demanding projects.<br></li><li><strong>Advanced Hydraulics:</strong>Features advanced hydraulic systems for precise control and enhanced performance in earth-moving and grading tasks.<br></li><li><strong>Operator Comfort:</strong>Designed with an ergonomic cabin and controls to ensure comfort and ease of use for operators during long work hours.<br></li><li><strong>Versatile Applications:</strong>Suitable for a wide range of heavy construction tasks including site preparation, grading, and material handling.<br></li></ul><p>Ideal for large-scale construction projects, the Durable Bulldozer by Komatsu offers exceptional performance and durability, providing reliable support for various heavy-duty tasks and contributing to efficient construction operations.</p>', 99999999.99, '1723004944_7cfa86502e9de48d6114.png', 'Samarinda', 10, NULL);
INSERT INTO `products` VALUES (42, 'Liebherr Crane', '<h2>High-Capacity Crane for Lifting and Construction</h2><p>The High-Capacity Crane by Liebherr is engineered to provide exceptional lifting power and reliability for construction and industrial applications. Designed to handle heavy loads with precision and safety, this crane is ideal for large-scale construction projects, including building infrastructure, lifting heavy materials, and managing complex lifting tasks.<br>Its advanced design and robust construction ensure it can operate efficiently in demanding environments, offering versatility and strength for a wide range of lifting and construction needs.</p><br><h3>Key Features:</h3><ul><li><strong>High Capacity:</strong>Capable of lifting and handling extremely heavy loads, making it suitable for large-scale construction and industrial tasks.<br></li><li><strong>Advanced Technology:</strong>Incorporates cutting-edge technology for enhanced lifting precision, stability, and safety.<br></li><li><strong>Robust Construction:</strong>Built with durable materials and engineering to withstand the rigors of heavy lifting and demanding construction environments.<br></li><li><strong>Versatile Applications:</strong>Ideal for various construction and industrial applications, including infrastructure development, material handling, and large-scale lifting operations.<br></li><li><strong>Operator Safety and Comfort:</strong>Designed with safety features and a comfortable operator cabin to ensure efficient and safe operation during extended use.<br></li></ul><p>Perfect for heavy lifting and construction projects, the High-Capacity Crane by Liebherr delivers powerful performance and reliability, supporting a wide range of lifting and construction activities with its advanced features and robust design.</p>', 99999999.99, '1723005062_aaae2ad1447cf11720f9.jpg', 'Solo', 10, NULL);
INSERT INTO `products` VALUES (43, 'Jungheinrich Electric Forklift', '<h2>Electric Forklift for Efficient Warehouse Handling</h2><p>The Electric Forklift by Jungheinrich is designed to provide efficient and reliable performance for warehouse and material handling operations. With its advanced electric drive system, this forklift offers smooth, quiet, and energy-efficient operation, making it ideal for indoor use in warehouses and distribution centers.<br>Its compact design and maneuverability make it well-suited for navigating tight spaces and handling various loads, contributing to improved productivity and operational efficiency in warehouse environments.</p><br><h3>Key Features:</h3><ul><li><strong>Energy Efficient:</strong>Powered by an advanced electric drive system that minimizes energy consumption and reduces operating costs.<br></li><li><strong>Quiet Operation:</strong>Operates quietly, making it suitable for use in noise-sensitive environments such as indoor warehouses.<br></li><li><strong>Compact Design:</strong>Features a space-saving design that allows for easy maneuverability in tight aisles and crowded warehouse spaces.<br></li><li><strong>High Performance:</strong>Provides reliable lifting and handling capabilities, enhancing productivity and efficiency in material handling tasks.<br></li><li><strong>Enhanced Safety:</strong>Equipped with safety features such as stability controls and ergonomic controls to ensure safe and comfortable operation.<br></li></ul><p>Ideal for warehouse and distribution center operations, the Electric Forklift by Jungheinrich offers superior performance, efficiency, and safety, supporting efficient material handling and contributing to a streamlined warehouse operation.</p>', 32000000.00, '1723005158_13db9ad716c1c8c2ba26.jpg', 'Batam', 10, NULL);
INSERT INTO `products` VALUES (44, 'Hyster Container Handler', '<h2>Container Handler for Port and Shipping Operations</h2><p>The Container Handler by Hyster is specifically designed to manage and transport shipping containers efficiently within port and shipping environments. Engineered for robust performance and reliability, this container handler excels in lifting, stacking, and moving containers of various sizes and weights. It is ideal for use in busy ports and shipping yards, where speed and precision are crucial for maintaining smooth operations.<br>With its advanced features and durable construction, this container handler supports effective port logistics and contributes to streamlined shipping operations.</p><br><h3>Key Features:</h3><ul><li><strong>High Capacity:</strong>Capable of handling heavy and large containers, making it suitable for demanding port and shipping operations.<br></li><li><strong>Advanced Lifting Mechanism:</strong>Equipped with a sophisticated lifting system for precise and efficient container handling.<br></li><li><strong>Durable Construction:</strong>Built to withstand the harsh conditions of port environments and provide long-term reliability.<br></li><li><strong>Enhanced Maneuverability:</strong>Designed for ease of maneuvering in tight spaces and crowded areas within ports and shipping yards.<br></li><li><strong>Operator Comfort and Safety:</strong>Features an ergonomic cabin and safety controls to ensure comfortable and secure operation for the driver.<br></li></ul><p>Perfect for port and shipping operations, the Container Handler by Hyster offers exceptional performance, durability, and efficiency, facilitating effective container management and supporting seamless shipping logistics.</p>', 99999999.99, '1723005220_338624b9482e0f03b939.webp', 'Cirebon', 10, NULL);
INSERT INTO `products` VALUES (45, 'Sungrow Solar Inverter', '<h2>Reliable Solar Inverter for Photovoltaic Systems</h2><p>The Reliable Solar Inverter by Sungrow is designed to provide efficient and stable conversion of solar energy in photovoltaic systems. This inverter ensures optimal performance by converting direct current (DC) from solar panels into alternating current (AC) for use in residential and commercial applications. Engineered for reliability and efficiency, it supports various photovoltaic system configurations and enhances overall energy production.<br>With its advanced technology and robust design, this solar inverter contributes to maximizing energy yields and ensuring consistent power supply from solar installations.</p><br><h3>Key Features:</h3><ul><li><strong>High Efficiency:</strong>Delivers excellent energy conversion efficiency, maximizing the power output from photovoltaic systems.<br></li><li><strong>Advanced Technology:</strong>Incorporates state-of-the-art technology for reliable performance and enhanced energy management.<br></li><li><strong>Durable Design:</strong>Built with high-quality materials to ensure long-term reliability and withstand various environmental conditions.<br></li><li><strong>Versatile Compatibility:</strong>Supports a wide range of photovoltaic system configurations and panel types, providing flexibility in installation.<br></li><li><strong>User-Friendly Interface:</strong>Features an intuitive interface for easy monitoring and management of solar energy production.<br></li></ul><p>Ideal for both residential and commercial photovoltaic systems, the Reliable Solar Inverter by Sungrow offers superior performance and durability, enhancing the efficiency and reliability of solar energy conversion and contributing to sustainable energy solutions.</p>', 1600000.00, '1723005263_bda10fc140caf1fe2bf1.webp', 'Kendari', 10, NULL);
INSERT INTO `products` VALUES (46, 'Trina Solar Panels', '<h2>High-Efficiency Solar Panels for Energy Generation</h2><p>The High-Efficiency Solar Panels by Trina are engineered to provide superior energy generation for photovoltaic systems. Designed with cutting-edge technology, these panels offer high efficiency in converting sunlight into electricity, maximizing energy output and minimizing space requirements. Ideal for both residential and commercial solar installations, they ensure reliable and cost-effective solar energy production.<br>Their advanced design and durable construction make them well-suited for various environmental conditions, contributing to long-term performance and energy savings.</p><br><h3>Key Features:</h3><ul><li><strong>High Efficiency:</strong>Provides exceptional energy conversion rates, generating more electricity from the same amount of sunlight.<br></li><li><strong>Advanced Technology:</strong>Utilizes state-of-the-art solar cell technology for enhanced performance and reliability.<br></li><li><strong>Durable Construction:</strong>Built with high-quality materials to withstand various weather conditions and ensure long-term durability.<br></li><li><strong>Versatile Applications:</strong>Suitable for both residential and commercial solar installations, offering flexibility in deployment.<br></li><li><strong>Enhanced Performance:</strong>Designed to deliver consistent performance and high energy yield over the lifespan of the panels.<br></li></ul><p>Ideal for optimizing energy production in solar systems, the High-Efficiency Solar Panels by Trina offer excellent performance and reliability, supporting effective energy generation and contributing to sustainable energy solutions.</p>', 4200000.00, '1723005355_b146a9cc7e452176afde.png', 'Tangerang', 10, NULL);

